cs.SI, cs.SD, cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.CY 

Reasoning: 
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is the most likely category as the paper deals with analyzing data from social network services to estimate similarity between brands. 
- cs.SD (Software Engineering) is also a likely category as the paper proposes a new algorithm to analyze data and calculate similarity between brands. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is another possible category as the paper deals with analyzing text data (hashtags) to estimate similarity between brands. 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is a possible category as the paper deals with natural language processing (NLP) to analyze text data. 
- cs.CY (Computers and Society) is a possible category as the paper deals with the impact of social media on sales and customer behavior.
